query:
SELECT 
  supplierId,
  COUNT(*) as total_rows,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN isServiceable = 1 THEN 1 END) as serviceable_1,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN isServiceable = 0 THEN 1 END) as serviceable_0,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN isServiceable IS NULL THEN 1 END) as serviceable_null
FROM supplierRates 
GROUP BY supplierId
HAVING total_rows = 348;
